posts.post_title: FS: Multi-Strike Back and Multi Print Front Dave Brain**SOLD***
posts.post_content:
For sale is a Dave Brain with a multi-strike back and multi-print front. It is labeled only as a Multi Strike as that was all SGC would do at the time. This may be a step below the Bernhard just sold but with the multi-print front it is quite unique. At this time I am fielding offers but no trades. 

Feel free to send me a PM or Email for more information.

Thanks,
Adam
Thanks guys. Hate to move but it would help my current endeavor !!

Adam,

Very Cool! I wish that I could afford it; unfortunately even with working 18 hour days, I have a feeling I still will come up short.

I will keep working hard though and maybe some day, just maybe some day, it will rest in my T206 collection.

Take care Charlie
